attributes.Long form description: The student's task is to operate the ATV. The first thing he does is to change the transmission of the lever to neutral, then he approaches to the lever arm to insert it into the peg, once placed, he goes to the parts bin to take a washer and a bolt, however, he has difficulty finding the correct bolt, once the instructor tells him which one to take, the student goes back to the ATV to take from the tool cart a ratchet to screw the lever arm to the peg with the bolt and washer.  Then, he approaches the lever and starts to change it to all the different transmissions, once he finishes, he turns on the electrical lift table to raise and lower it with the remote, once this is done, he goes to the lever and starts to change transmissions again. once this is done, he approaches the lever arm and unscrews the bolt, once he unscrews it, he removes it and puts it back in the parts bin. Then he approaches to the ATV to remove the lever arm from the peg, finally, he picks up the lever to change the transmission to neutral.
